'''水上伯顿'''（{{lang-en|Bourton-on-the-Water}}）是[[英格兰|英格兰]]西南部[[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]][[科茨沃尔德区|科茨沃尔德区]]的一个村庄，位于一个宽平的谷地，属于[[科茨沃尔德|科茨沃尔德]][[杰出自然风景区|杰出自然风景区]]的一部分。2011年有人口 3,296 人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11120973&c=Bourton-on-the-Water&d=16&e=62&g=6426904&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1427022251873&enc=1|title=Parish population 2011|accessdate=22 March 2015|archive-date=1 September 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901105732/https://www.ons.gov.uk/help/localstatistics}}</ref>村庄中心沿河地带的大部分为指定的保护区<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cotswold.gov.uk/media/451014/Conservation-area-statement-Bourton.pdf|title=Conservation Area Statement|publisher=Cotswold District Council|accessdate=16 July 2018|archive-date=17 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717013202/https://www.cotswold.gov.uk/media/451014/Conservation-area-statement-Bourton.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Most Sustainable Principal Settlements: Bourton-on-the-Water|publisher=Cotswold District Council|year=2001|work=Cotswold Local Plan|url=http://www.localplan.cotswold.gov.uk/localplan/text/text08.htm|accessdate=2 July 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111107050134/http://www.localplan.cotswold.gov.uk/localplan/text/text08.htm#|archivedate=7 November 2011}}</ref>。

[[File:Bourton_on_the_water_map_7909.jpg|thumb]]
水上伯顿街道两侧是又长又宽的绿地， Windrush河贯穿其中。河上有五座石拱桥，建于1654年至1953年之间，因此被称为“科茨沃尔德的威尼斯”<ref>{{cite web|title=History of Bourton-on-the-Water|website=Cotswolds Info|url=https://www.cotswolds.info/blogs/bourton-on-the-water.shtml|accessdate=16 July 2018|archive-date=21 June 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621012133/http://www.cotswolds.info/blogs/bourton-on-the-water.shtml}}</ref>。
[[File:St_lawrence_bourton_7897.jpg|thumb]]

在旅游旺季，该村的游客往往比居民多。<ref>{{cite web|title=Local Plan|publisher=Cotswold District Council|url=http://www.localplan.cotswold.gov.uk/localplan/text/text08.htm|accessdate=2 July 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111107050134/http://www.localplan.cotswold.gov.uk/localplan/text/text08.htm#|archive-date=7 November 2011}}</ref>每年约有30万游客抵达，而常住居民不到3500人<ref>{{cite web|title=12 tiny villages which are drowning in tourists|work=Daily Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/galleries/villages-where-tourists-outnumber-locals/Bourton/|accessdate=16 July 2018|archive-date=16 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716224125/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/galleries/villages-where-tourists-outnumber-locals/Bourton/}}</ref>。

水上伯顿有两座教堂，浸信会教堂和圣公会圣劳伦斯堂（St Lawrence），后者是保护建筑，平时向公众开放，它建于14世纪，18世纪主要部分进行了改建<ref>{{cite web|title=St Lawrence Church|publisher=British Listed Buildings|url=https://www.britishlistedbuildings.co.uk/101170801-church-of-st-lawrence-bourton-on-the-water|accessdate=16 July 2018|archive-date=17 July 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180717012949/https://www.britishlistedbuildings.co.uk/101170801-church-of-st-lawrence-bourton-on-the-water}}</ref>。

[[File:Bourton-on-the-Water_2010_PD_09.JPG|thumb]]
